@model IEnumerable<上海燕洵物联网科技有限公司人事管理系统.Models.VacateViewModel>
@using 上海燕洵物联网科技有限公司人事管理系统.Controllers

@{
    ViewBag.Title = "显示员工请假信息";
}
<script src="~/Content/jquery-3.1.1.js"></script>
<link href="~/Areas/layer/mobile/need/layer.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<script src="~/Areas/layer/layer.js"></script>
<h2>显示个人请假信息</h2>
<span>总记录数<span id="totaldata">@ViewBag.totaldata</span>条</span>
<table class="table">
    <tr>
        <th>
            员工编号
        </th>
        <th>
            员工姓名
        </th>
        <th>
            请假原因
        </th>
        <th>
            请假描述
        </th>
        <th>
            请假状态
        </th>

    </tr>

    @foreach (var item in Model)
    {
        <tr>
            <td>
                @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.EmpsId)
            </td>
            <td>
                @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Name)
            </td>
            <td>
                @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Cause)
            </td>
            <td>
                @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Remark)
            </td>
            <td>
                @{StateInfo s = (StateInfo)item.VacateState;}
                @s
            </td>



        </tr>
    }

</table>
<p>
    <span>
        <span>当前第</span>
        <span id="currentindex">@ViewBag.currentindex</span>
        <span>页，总共</span>
        <span id="totalpage">@ViewBag.totalpage</span>
        <span>页</span>

    </span>
    <input id="BtnUp" type="button" value="上一页" onclick="BtnUp()" />
    <input id="BtnDown" type="button" value="下一页" onclick="BtnDown()" />
</p>
<script>
    $(function () {
        $("#totalpage").text(Math.ceil((Number($("#totaldata").text()) / 5)));
    })
    function BtnUp() {
        if ($("#currentindex").text() != 1) {
            location.href = "/Emps/ShowVacate?pageindex=" + Number(Number($("#currentindex").text()) - 1);
        }
        else {
            layer.alert('已经是首页了');           
        }
    }
    function BtnDown() {
        if ($("#currentindex").text() != $("#totalpage").text()) {
            location.href = "/Emps/ShowVacate?pageindex=" + Number(Number($("#currentindex").text()) + 1);
        }
        else {
            layer.alert('已经是尾页了');
        }
    }

    fun();
    function fun() {
        $("[name=Menu]").empty();
        $.ajax({
            url: "../Login/ShowMenu",
            contentType: "application/json",
            dataType: "json",
            success: function (data) {
                console.log(data);
                var li = '';
                for (var i in data) {
                    li += '  <li><a href="' + data[i].href + '"><i class="fa fa-edit"></i><span>' + data[i].PermissionName + '</span></a></li>';
                }
                $("[name=Menu]").append(li);
            }

        })


    }
    function Del(Id, obj) {
        $.ajax({
            url: "/Manager/DeleteVacate?Id=" + Id,
            success: function (data) {
                layer.alert(data);
                $(obj).parent().parent().remove();
                $("#totaldata").text(Number(Number($("#totaldata").text()) - 1))
            }

        })
    }
</script>


